refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public arrayGmagick::getimageboundingbox floatfuzz
Computes the bounding box, the smallest rectangle enclosing the image content that differs from the border color, using fuzz as the color-matching tolerance.

&reftitle.parameters;
fuzz
The fuzz factor; colors within this distance of the border color are treated as part of the border. Larger values match a broader range of colors.
